{
  "chapter": 49,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十九回 有子万事足。新年雪地，小方从宿醉中醒来，看到一对父子买泥娃娃，想起苏苏已怀了他的孩子，心情前所未有的开朗。但回到客栈发现苏苏已失踪，屋里一片狼藉。小方精神崩溃，开始酗酒度日，直到被打断肋骨。醒来后发现被吕三安排在温柔乡中，文雀奉命服侍他。小方挣脱逃离，却在街头被赵群拦住。赵群当众揭露苏苏怀了小方的孩子，小方当众承认。酒后对质中，小方揭穿赵群就是吕三本人。吕三坦然承认，道出报复缘由——小方杀了他儿子，所以他要用苏苏腹中的孩子来偿还。吕三展示绝对掌控：小方的名声、母亲、朋友、情人、孩子全部落入他手。吕三抛出魔眼剑让小方拼命，小方却无力拾起。吕三又召出杀手麻雀——一个轻功绝高、独创金刚啄的可怕人物，让小方彻底绝望。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "店主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "年年平安，事事如意。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是谁？怎么会睡在我旁边？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_que",
      "speaker_name": "文雀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我叫文雀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_que",
      "speaker_name": "文雀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是你的朋友要我来陪你的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wen_que",
      "text": "我那朋友是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_que",
      "speaker_name": "文雀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是吕三爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_que",
      "speaker_name": "文雀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这里是我的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_que",
      "speaker_name": "文雀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "随便你高兴在这里住多久都行。你的朋友已经替你把所有的账都付过了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_que",
      "speaker_name": "文雀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这里还有酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_que",
      "speaker_name": "文雀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "花雕、茅台、大曲、竹叶青，随便你要喝什么，这里都有，所以你绝不能走。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_que",
      "speaker_name": "文雀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我知道你绝不会走的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_que",
      "speaker_name": "文雀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "吕三爷也知道你绝不会走的，他……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "赵群。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你还没有死。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "想不到我们居然都没有死。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "苏苏呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "苏苏为什么没有跟你在一起？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你瘦了，而且好像病了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这些日子来，你一定遭遇到很多很可怕的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不管怎么样，那些事现在都已经过去了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "今天我刚巧约了很多朋友，那些朋友一定也会认得你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我的朋友，就是你的朋友，你一定要去。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位一定听说过，江湖中有个要命的小方。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这朋友就是要命的小方。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我可以向各位保证，他绝对是个好朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜鹰是他的好朋友，我也是，我们都曾经救过他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们都信任他，甚至将自己未来的妻子都交托给他。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是现在我的妻子已经有了他的孩子。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我说的是不是真话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你承认？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "我承认。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "我承认，我承认…",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你在想什么？是不是有什么话要对我说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "不是我有话要对你说。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "是你有话要对我说。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "有件事你早就应该告诉我了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "你还记不记得那个穿白衣，饮烈酒，唱悲歌的歌者？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我记得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我当然记得。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "我们埋葬了他之后，在苏苏为“阳光”治伤的时候，在那个山坡上，你是不是对我说过，有件秘密要告诉我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "但是你一直都没有告诉我。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我没有。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我一直都没有机会说出来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "现在你也已经用不着说出来了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "因为我已经知道你要说的是什么。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "因为现在我已经知道你是谁了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你知道我是谁？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你说，我是谁？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "你就是吕三。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你怎么知道我就是吕三？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "其实我知道你迟早总是会想到的。你并不太笨，现在也是你应该知道的时候。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不错。我就是吕三。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你当然早就知道“赵群”这个名字是假的，这张脸也是假的。所以你现在虽然知道我就是吕三，但是等到你下次见到吕三时，还是没法子认得出来。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "还有下次？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "这一次还不是最后一次？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "还不是。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "是不是因为你还不想让我死得太快了？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "千古艰难惟一死，谁都不想死，只不过有时候死了反而比活着好得多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我相信你一定也知道这道理。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你知不知道我为什么把苏苏留下来给你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为你杀了我的儿子。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以我也要你还给我一个儿子，你自己亲生的儿子。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你已经完了，彻底完了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你在江湖中的名声已经完了。你的母亲、你的朋友、你的情人、你的儿子，都已经落入我手里。只要我高兴，随便我用什么法子对付他们都行。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是你永远都想像不到我会用什么法子对付他们，所以你只有往最坏的地方去想，越想越痛苦，不想又不行的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你还没有死，只不过因为我根本已不必杀你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为现在你活着远比死更痛苦得多。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "如果你认为你还有一口气，还可以跟我拼命的话，你就更错了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你不信？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "那么我不妨就让你试一试。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这是你的剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这柄剑，本来也是我的，现在我还给你。你既然还有一口气，你不妨就用这柄剑来跟我拼一拼。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 479
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "其实我早就知道你不会伸手的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为你自己也知道，只要一伸手抓起这把剑，你就死定了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在你活着虽然痛苦，可惜又偏偏不想死。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "死了什么都完了，现在你多多少少还有一点希望。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你心里说不定还在盼望着，卜鹰、班察巴那他们说不定还会跑来救你。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可惜就算他们真的来了，也一样没有用的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_ma_que",
      "text": "你不妨告诉他，你是什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_que",
      "speaker_name": "麻雀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我不是人，我是一只鸟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_que",
      "speaker_name": "麻雀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我的名字叫麻雀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_que",
      "speaker_name": "麻雀",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你也过来看看，看看他是不是真的已经做好了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    }
